    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh okay so it's mostly a visual thing. i was thinking about how they seem to \"meet\" up in the sky. if you have a bunch of planets all lining up at once, is that basically just a massive gathering or something? and why does it look so much different depending on where we are in our orbit?",
